description: From selling rotting seaweed to putting Mayo on the map, Mr Biden's Irish ancestors were a busy lot.
title: Joe Biden: Election fever and the Bidens' Irish relatives
title_page: Joe Biden: Election fever and the Bidens' Irish relatives - BBC News
maintext: Her family have been aware of their connection to the US politician for decades, but Ms Blewitt says: "The media only began to take notice when he became vice president."
